flowchart TD
  Pom[pom.xml] --> OpenApiGen[OpenAPI Generator executions]
  OpenApiGen --> GeneratedServer[target/generated-sources server interfaces]
  OpenApiGen --> GeneratedClients[target/generated-sources peer clients]
  Source[src/main/java handwritten code] --> MavenPackage[Maven package]
  GeneratedServer --> MavenPackage
  GeneratedClients --> MavenPackage
  Resources[application*.properties and db/changelog] --> MavenPackage
  MavenPackage --> Jar[AgencyService.jar]
  Jar --> Dockerfile
  Dockerfile --> Image[Container image]
  RuntimeEnv[Env vars: DB, Keycloak, Matrix, service URLs] --> Image
  Image --> K8s[Kubernetes or local runtime]
  K8s --> Actuator[/actuator/health]
